  m_Name: SO_Dialogue_StoreRoomDishesAfterCobwebs
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  background: {fileID: 0}
  lines:
  - speakerName: "V\u0169"
    englishSpeakerName: Vu
    text: "H\u1EBFt d\u1ECDn nh\u00E0 kho, c\u00F2n \u0111\u1EBFn \u0111\u1ED1ng b\u00E1t \u0111\u0169a n\u1EEFa... haizz."
    englishText: The storage room is done, and now there is that pile of dishes too... sigh.
    portrait: {fileID: -4254258901546231152, guid: c5d997eca51e38d418373f1e8fdc90ce, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Silly
    englishSpeakerName: Silly
    text: "\u01A0, th\u1EBF m\u00ECnh s\u1EBD d\u1ECDn h\u1EBFt b\u00E1t \u0111\u0169a cho c\u1EADu ch\u1EE7 lu\u00F4n."
    englishText: Oh, then I will clean all the dishes for him too.
    portrait: {fileID: 6468568510307345621, guid: 0c05e137063d43e429af4b01ffae35ac, type: 3}
